# Culture Hub API - Testes
# Use REST Client extension no VS Code

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Cadastro
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/cadastro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Obter Perfil (requer token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Listar Eventos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/eventos

### Listar Eventos com Filtros
GET http://localhost:3000/api/eventos?categoria=Musica&page=1&limit=5

### Buscar Evento Específico
GET http://localhost:3000/api/eventos/ID_DO_EVENTO

### Criar Evento (requer token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "tituloEvento": "Festival de Música",
  "descricao": "Grande festival de música ao ar livre",
  "categoria": "Musica",
  "dataInicio": "2025-08-15T18:00:00",
  "dataFim": "2025-08-15T23:00:00",
  "localizacao": "Parque Ibirapuera, São Paulo",
  "preco": 50,
  "capacidade": 1000
}

### Atualizar Evento (requer token)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/eventos/ID_DO_EVENTO
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "preco": 45,
  "disponibilidade": "Disponivel"
}

### Deletar Evento (requer token)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/eventos/ID_DO_EVENTO
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Inscrever em Evento
POST http://localhost:3000/api/eventos/ID_DO_EVENTO/inscrever
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": "ID_DO_USUARIO"
}

### Cancelar Inscrição
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/eventos/ID_DO_EVENTO/inscrever
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usuarioId": "ID_DO_USUARIO"
}

### Listar Usuários
GET http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios?page=1&limit=10

### Buscar Usuário
GET http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios/ID_DO_USUARIO

### Atualizar Perfil (requer token)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios/ID_DO_USUARIO
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "name": "João Silva Santos",
  "picture": "https://example.com/nova-foto.jpg"
}

### Eventos do Usuário
GET http://localhost:3000/api/usuarios/ID_DO_USUARIO/eventos
